1
00:00:06,272 --> 00:00:06,952
Lu,

2
00:00:08,032 --> 00:00:09,311
I called you here today

3
00:00:10,032 --> 00:00:11,272
to tell you something.

4
00:00:12,392 --> 00:00:14,471
Over all these years,

5
00:00:15,631 --> 00:00:17,272
I've never made you face

6
00:00:17,832 --> 00:00:20,391
and I'll never make you face

7
00:00:20,752 --> 00:00:22,552
an impossible choice.

8
00:00:23,592 --> 00:00:24,191
You,

9
00:00:24,752 --> 00:00:25,432
I,

10
00:00:25,712 --> 00:00:26,432
and Jiasheng

11
00:00:27,232 --> 00:00:30,151
are brothers bound by oath.

12
00:00:31,272 --> 00:00:32,151
At the very worst,

13
00:00:33,631 --> 00:00:35,392
even if someday he and I

14
00:00:35,631 --> 00:00:36,552
become irreconcilable

15
00:00:36,552 --> 00:00:37,592
like fire and water,

16
00:00:38,671 --> 00:00:40,152
it shouldn't affect you two.

17
00:00:41,872 --> 00:00:44,232
You two will always be
the best of friends,

18
00:00:44,751 --> 00:00:46,152
the most seamless partners.

19
00:00:49,431 --> 00:00:50,991
What are you even talking about?

20
00:00:53,031 --> 00:00:54,232
I came this time

21
00:00:54,952 --> 00:00:56,472
to get some clarity from you.

22
00:00:57,751 --> 00:00:59,472
What exactly happened between you two?

23
00:01:00,391 --> 00:01:01,391
Really want to know?

24
00:01:02,031 --> 00:01:02,592
Yes.

25
00:01:03,952 --> 00:01:04,512
Alright.

26
00:01:05,832 --> 00:01:06,912
Then I'll

27
00:01:07,272 --> 00:01:09,071
tell you everything exactly
as it happened.

28
00:01:09,872 --> 00:01:11,992
It all started

29
00:01:12,551 --> 00:01:14,872
from Jiasheng

30
00:01:15,632 --> 00:01:18,072
casting aside my father's

31
00:01:18,072 --> 00:01:20,471
lifelong reputation years ago.

32
00:01:21,792 --> 00:01:25,872
He turned a blind eye
as I was forced into exile,

33
00:01:26,671 --> 00:01:28,872
left me in agony,

34
00:01:28,872 --> 00:01:31,152
no way to live,

35
00:01:32,271 --> 00:01:34,952
or to die.

36
00:01:36,103 --> 00:01:38,400
=The Glory Fades=

37
00:01:39,040 --> 00:01:41,376
=Episode 29=
(The Diversion Trick)

38
00:01:51,391 --> 00:01:52,352
(From: Captain Liu, Security Dept.)
(Two hours ago,)

39
00:01:52,352 --> 00:01:53,671
(Lu received a letter.)

40
00:01:54,031 --> 00:01:55,831
(Inside was a childhood group photo.)

41
00:01:56,152 --> 00:01:58,551
(Then, he got a call
and left immediately.)

42
00:02:04,271 --> 00:02:05,432
I made two more drinks.

43
00:02:05,432 --> 00:02:06,592
Shall we continue, Mr. Tu?

44
00:02:12,191 --> 00:02:12,831
Mr. Tu?

45
00:02:14,472 --> 00:02:15,111
Mr. Tu?

46
00:02:37,831 --> 00:02:38,551
Chu Bai.

47
00:02:40,352 --> 00:02:41,072
You got it?

48
00:02:43,072 --> 00:02:46,151
Ruoxi mentioned in her diary
Tu Jiasheng can't hold his liquor well.

49
00:02:46,671 --> 00:02:49,072
In the drinks I mixed that day,
I doubled the whiskey.

50
00:02:50,752 --> 00:02:51,671
Smart move.

51
00:02:52,271 --> 00:02:53,111
Good that you got it.

52
00:02:53,271 --> 00:02:54,032
With this,

53
00:02:54,352 --> 00:02:55,831
I can bypass the final security layer

54
00:02:55,831 --> 00:02:56,912
and retrieve those files.

55
00:03:00,472 --> 00:03:01,072
Chu Bai,

56
00:03:01,792 --> 00:03:03,671
is this very risky?

57
00:03:07,671 --> 00:03:08,271
Yes.

58
00:03:09,711 --> 00:03:10,391
It's fine.

59
00:03:10,391 --> 00:03:11,111
I'm not afraid.

60
00:03:12,072 --> 00:03:13,551
If I can bring him to justice

61
00:03:13,671 --> 00:03:14,632
and avenge your sister,

62
00:03:14,952 --> 00:03:15,792
all is worth it.

63
00:03:19,271 --> 00:03:21,271
But in my view,

64
00:03:21,912 --> 00:03:23,151
he truly loved Ruoxi.

65
00:03:24,151 --> 00:03:25,352
I studied psychology.

66
00:03:25,831 --> 00:03:27,632
His eyes and micro-expressions
couldn't lie.

67
00:03:28,671 --> 00:03:29,312
However,

68
00:03:29,551 --> 00:03:30,591
anyway,

69
00:03:31,232 --> 00:03:32,111
thank you.

70
00:03:32,831 --> 00:03:33,512
It's nothing.

71
00:03:34,792 --> 00:03:35,431
By the way,

72
00:03:36,391 --> 00:03:37,752
regarding Tu Jiasheng's alibi

73
00:03:37,752 --> 00:03:39,192
for the day Ruoxi died,

74
00:03:39,192 --> 00:03:40,072
how did he explain it?

75
00:03:40,271 --> 00:03:41,032
Is it credible?

76
00:03:41,472 --> 00:03:42,312
He claimed

77
00:03:42,671 --> 00:03:44,671
he never went to her villa at all.

78
00:03:45,871 --> 00:03:46,512
As expected.

79
00:03:47,711 --> 00:03:48,391
Expected what?

80
00:03:49,711 --> 00:03:50,232
Nothing.

81
00:03:50,711 --> 00:03:51,711
I mean,

82
00:03:52,151 --> 00:03:53,391
he predictably didn't admit it.

83
00:03:56,472 --> 00:03:58,111
From my investigation these days,

84
00:03:58,551 --> 00:04:00,512
I found Tu Jiasheng has been secretly

85
00:04:00,831 --> 00:04:03,632
buying and selling official positions,
and taking and giving bribes.

86
00:04:04,151 --> 00:04:05,111
These transactions

87
00:04:05,472 --> 00:04:06,912
are handled by 'hostesses'

88
00:04:06,912 --> 00:04:08,991
at Deep In The Bustle,
who act as intermediaries.

89
00:04:09,151 --> 00:04:10,391
The funds are then

90
00:04:10,831 --> 00:04:14,551
loaded onto prepaid cards
and funneled into Deep In The Bustle.

91
00:04:14,752 --> 00:04:16,472
Tu Jiasheng then redistributes them.

92
00:04:17,072 --> 00:04:17,912
I suspect

93
00:04:18,591 --> 00:04:20,192
the evidence we're looking for,

94
00:04:20,591 --> 00:04:22,072
namely, the ones Ruoxi found,

95
00:04:22,752 --> 00:04:24,151
are the transaction videos

96
00:04:24,151 --> 00:04:24,952
and the ledger.

97
00:04:47,591 --> 00:04:48,471
Here, try it.

98
00:04:49,152 --> 00:04:50,336
You've never had it before.

99
00:04:50,711 --> 00:04:51,471
It's selective.

100
00:04:57,471 --> 00:04:58,151
Not bad.

101
00:04:59,672 --> 00:05:00,711
Do you know its price?

102
00:05:05,552 --> 00:05:06,591
So expensive.

103
00:05:08,351 --> 00:05:09,512
For those who don't like it,

104
00:05:10,031 --> 00:05:10,992
it's worth nothing.

105
00:05:11,351 --> 00:05:12,432
For those who like it,

106
00:05:12,552 --> 00:05:13,512
it's hard to get.

107
00:05:14,031 --> 00:05:14,872
The same tea

108
00:05:14,872 --> 00:05:16,312
tastes different

109
00:05:16,591 --> 00:05:18,752
and has a different value
to different people.

110
00:05:27,512 --> 00:05:28,151
Jiasheng,

111
00:05:28,831 --> 00:05:29,752
I don't understand tea.

112
00:05:30,552 --> 00:05:32,151
But I have my own judging standards.

113
00:05:36,552 --> 00:05:38,512
If you get used to it,
it should be good.

114
00:05:40,151 --> 00:05:40,711
Right.

115
00:05:41,231 --> 00:05:41,952
Don't rush.

116
00:05:42,072 --> 00:05:42,831
Taste carefully.

117
00:05:43,672 --> 00:05:44,351
Take a taste

118
00:05:44,632 --> 00:05:46,072
and you'll know its flavor.

119
00:05:48,992 --> 00:05:49,791
You're right.

120
00:05:50,391 --> 00:05:51,831
Tea must be savored slowly.

121
00:05:59,072 --> 00:05:59,711
By the way,

122
00:06:00,231 --> 00:06:01,112
you said

123
00:06:01,112 --> 00:06:02,471
Ruoxi left something for you.

124
00:06:02,831 --> 00:06:04,112
You must keep it safe.

125
00:06:04,552 --> 00:06:05,632
I think inside it

126
00:06:05,791 --> 00:06:07,231
may be crucial evidence.

127
00:06:08,351 --> 00:06:09,151
Rest assured.

128
00:06:09,432 --> 00:06:10,271
It's all stored away.

129
00:06:12,192 --> 00:06:12,711
By the way,

130
00:06:13,672 --> 00:06:14,351
read this.

131
00:06:19,471 --> 00:06:22,112
(Custom Design Drawing)
The wristband they custom-made?

132
00:06:23,192 --> 00:06:23,831
Exactly.

133
00:06:24,432 --> 00:06:26,192
I found old-timers around them
back then.

134
00:06:26,591 --> 00:06:27,911
Unexpectedly, from the craftsmen,

135
00:06:27,911 --> 00:06:29,271
I got the design drawings.

136
00:06:30,432 --> 00:06:31,391
There were

137
00:06:31,591 --> 00:06:32,831
three finished pieces

138
00:06:33,072 --> 00:06:34,072
and one sample.

139
00:06:34,672 --> 00:06:36,072
They took all of them.

140
00:06:36,752 --> 00:06:40,031
Unlike the finished ones,
the sample had no anti-counterfeit code.

141
00:06:45,471 --> 00:06:46,231
This tea

142
00:06:46,591 --> 00:06:48,312
has been fermented for years,

143
00:06:48,831 --> 00:06:50,752
so its taste can be a bit tricky.

144
00:06:51,952 --> 00:06:54,312
But because it's aged over time,

145
00:06:54,791 --> 00:06:56,031
there is

146
00:06:56,391 --> 00:06:57,391
a lingering fragrance,

147
00:06:57,632 --> 00:06:58,471
intriguing.

148
00:06:59,072 --> 00:07:01,391
Unlike some mass-produced sodas,

149
00:07:02,591 --> 00:07:03,992
even if they're old brands,

150
00:07:04,672 --> 00:07:06,471
they can only replicate past flavors

151
00:07:06,952 --> 00:07:08,552
just to satisfy people's nostalgia.

152
00:07:10,952 --> 00:07:12,031
Their commercial purpose

153
00:07:13,112 --> 00:07:14,192
is blatantly obvious.

154
00:07:20,471 --> 00:07:21,192
(How about it?)

155
00:07:21,752 --> 00:07:22,952
(Jiasheng)

156
00:07:23,072 --> 00:07:24,711
must have told you

157
00:07:25,072 --> 00:07:26,672
a completely different version, right?

158
00:07:29,031 --> 00:07:30,632
Don't hide it from me.

159
00:07:30,632 --> 00:07:31,752
I know everything.

160
00:07:32,192 --> 00:07:33,271
From the moment

161
00:07:33,271 --> 00:07:36,072
Jiasheng sensed I was coming back,

162
00:07:37,872 --> 00:07:38,672
I knew

163
00:07:39,952 --> 00:07:41,672
he would fabricate a story

164
00:07:42,231 --> 00:07:45,192
that completely distorts the past

165
00:07:46,031 --> 00:07:47,151
to tell you.

166
00:07:49,471 --> 00:07:50,432
But, Lu,

167
00:07:52,992 --> 00:07:53,992
I also know

168
00:07:54,791 --> 00:07:57,151
you don't fully trust him.

169
00:07:57,471 --> 00:07:58,112
Am I right?

170
00:08:01,072 --> 00:08:03,231
Drink it. Lose its fizz
and it'll spoil the flavor.

171
00:08:04,711 --> 00:08:05,911
Come on, take a sip of tea.

172
00:08:05,911 --> 00:08:07,552
It won't taste good once it cools down.

173
00:08:07,552 --> 00:08:08,052
Here.

174
00:08:25,791 --> 00:08:26,872
Another pot of hot tea.

175
00:08:27,952 --> 00:08:28,952
Gone, and forgotten.

176
00:08:29,351 --> 00:08:30,072
It's a bad omen.

177
00:08:35,112 --> 00:08:36,512
Forgetting or not

178
00:08:37,192 --> 00:08:38,351
depends on the relationship.

179
00:08:39,591 --> 00:08:41,672
Does it exist in Deep In The Bustle?

180
00:08:42,192 --> 00:08:42,751
Look.

181
00:08:43,351 --> 00:08:44,591
Feng has been gone for years,

182
00:08:45,351 --> 00:08:46,991
yet he still holds that top spot.

183
00:08:52,312 --> 00:08:53,631
That top spot

184
00:08:55,912 --> 00:08:56,991
only meant for Feng?

185
00:09:01,631 --> 00:09:02,871
I received a call.

186
00:09:03,432 --> 00:09:04,991
I met Feng last night.

187
00:09:16,192 --> 00:09:17,192
Let's go out and talk.

188
00:09:21,351 --> 00:09:22,072
Jiasheng,

189
00:09:22,831 --> 00:09:24,152
aren't you curious

190
00:09:24,152 --> 00:09:25,432
about what Feng told me?

191
00:09:28,072 --> 00:09:29,312
No matter what he said,

192
00:09:29,511 --> 00:09:30,751
we're still brothers.

193
00:09:31,192 --> 00:09:32,192
From the moment we

194
00:09:32,192 --> 00:09:34,032
kowtowed with our heads to the ground,

195
00:09:34,831 --> 00:09:35,591
it was set.

196
00:09:35,912 --> 00:09:37,511
It was etched in our bones.

197
00:09:39,751 --> 00:09:40,912
If not for Feng,

198
00:09:41,912 --> 00:09:43,192
I'd not have been who I am.

199
00:09:43,952 --> 00:09:44,831
I'll remember forever

200
00:09:45,312 --> 00:09:46,192
this bond.

201
00:09:47,991 --> 00:09:49,631
There was a man named

202
00:09:49,711 --> 00:09:51,392
Huang Weide.

203
00:09:52,192 --> 00:09:53,072
Ring any bells?

204
00:09:54,591 --> 00:09:56,072
Huang Weide from the Yanyue Gang?

205
00:09:56,711 --> 00:09:57,631
Bingo.

206
00:09:58,072 --> 00:09:58,952
Good memory.

207
00:09:59,351 --> 00:10:00,912
(Huang Weide)

208
00:10:00,912 --> 00:10:02,192
(was indeed arrogant,)

209
00:10:02,552 --> 00:10:03,912
(but you know)

210
00:10:04,231 --> 00:10:06,111
(the Yanyue Gang backing him)

211
00:10:06,111 --> 00:10:07,991
(was truly powerful.)

212
00:10:09,312 --> 00:10:11,111
(Who'd have thought)

213
00:10:11,111 --> 00:10:12,591
(for a woman,)

214
00:10:12,672 --> 00:10:14,751
(Jiasheng actually
took Huang Weide's life.)

215
00:10:15,392 --> 00:10:16,871
I know what happened later.

216
00:10:17,312 --> 00:10:17,912
I had people

217
00:10:17,912 --> 00:10:19,312
renovate Room 999.

218
00:10:20,471 --> 00:10:21,552
Jiasheng told me

219
00:10:22,111 --> 00:10:23,432
he fought against Huang Weide.

220
00:10:26,312 --> 00:10:27,152
So back then,

221
00:10:27,871 --> 00:10:29,511
you went abroad because you took

222
00:10:29,511 --> 00:10:30,471
the fall for this?

223
00:10:32,152 --> 00:10:33,032
Yeah.

224
00:10:33,672 --> 00:10:36,831
As we're brothers,
covering for each other is nothing.

225
00:10:36,991 --> 00:10:37,952
A minor issue.

226
00:10:38,952 --> 00:10:40,272
Plus, my father

227
00:10:40,272 --> 00:10:41,751
held considerable power.

228
00:10:42,111 --> 00:10:44,631
The other side didn't dare push too far.

229
00:10:46,471 --> 00:10:47,792
But I never expected

230
00:10:49,072 --> 00:10:50,471
Jiasheng would finally

231
00:10:50,912 --> 00:10:52,392
cross the line.

232
00:10:54,511 --> 00:10:56,152
He must have told you

233
00:10:56,991 --> 00:10:59,272
about that deal with Qin Wei back then.

234
00:11:01,631 --> 00:11:02,711
That deal

235
00:11:03,192 --> 00:11:05,552
was proposed by the Yanyue Gang.

236
00:11:05,912 --> 00:11:09,351
Yet Jiasheng firmly opposed it.

237
00:11:09,552 --> 00:11:11,912
He even kicked Qin Wei out.

238
00:11:15,231 --> 00:11:16,711
You don't understand.

239
00:11:16,711 --> 00:11:20,032
If that deal had gone through back then,

240
00:11:21,152 --> 00:11:22,711
I would have

241
00:11:22,711 --> 00:11:24,912
returned home openly

242
00:11:24,912 --> 00:11:27,471
and my father would've been safe too.

243
00:11:28,272 --> 00:11:29,152
However,

244
00:11:29,912 --> 00:11:31,912
because of his opposition,

245
00:11:32,111 --> 00:11:34,912
he made my father sick with rage.

246
00:11:36,032 --> 00:11:38,032
That made me even more afraid to return.

247
00:11:41,272 --> 00:11:41,912
Jiasheng,

248
00:11:43,991 --> 00:11:44,912
you know me.

249
00:11:45,192 --> 00:11:46,991
I've never cared
about family background.

250
00:11:47,952 --> 00:11:48,991
You're capable,

251
00:11:48,991 --> 00:11:49,831
ruthless

252
00:11:49,831 --> 00:11:50,511
and steady.

253
00:11:51,751 --> 00:11:52,792
You know when I started

254
00:11:52,792 --> 00:11:53,711
admiring you?

255
00:11:55,912 --> 00:11:56,831
When you turned down

256
00:11:56,831 --> 00:11:58,792
the Grand Princess's niece for Ruoxi,

257
00:11:59,631 --> 00:12:00,711
you're the man.

258
00:12:03,511 --> 00:12:04,991
Growing up in this circle,

259
00:12:05,991 --> 00:12:07,032
I know

260
00:12:07,032 --> 00:12:07,991
what people will do

261
00:12:08,192 --> 00:12:09,591
will do for things like money

262
00:12:09,591 --> 00:12:10,392
and power.

263
00:12:11,672 --> 00:12:13,111
Everyone wants to be top dog,

264
00:12:13,312 --> 00:12:14,312
only climbing up,

265
00:12:15,072 --> 00:12:15,991
not treating themselves

266
00:12:16,351 --> 00:12:17,432
nor others as human.

267
00:12:19,072 --> 00:12:20,072
I want to be a human,

268
00:12:21,231 --> 00:12:21,912
but I can't.

269
00:12:21,912 --> 00:12:22,792
I was born here.

270
00:12:25,631 --> 00:12:26,672
Anyway,

271
00:12:27,672 --> 00:12:28,672
I respect you most.

272
00:12:29,312 --> 00:12:30,231
Want you to know that.

273
00:12:36,631 --> 00:12:37,231
Lu,

274
00:12:38,631 --> 00:12:40,552
I've always treated you
like my real brother.

275
00:12:42,991 --> 00:12:43,912
That said,

276
00:12:45,111 --> 00:12:46,511
it's true Feng helped me rise

277
00:12:46,672 --> 00:12:48,032
and took the fall for me.

278
00:12:48,831 --> 00:12:51,072
My firm opposition to that deal
is also true.

279
00:12:51,711 --> 00:12:52,312
I think

280
00:12:53,272 --> 00:12:54,631
he must have told you too.

281
00:12:56,032 --> 00:12:56,631
Moreover,

282
00:12:57,032 --> 00:12:57,831
in recent years,

283
00:12:58,351 --> 00:12:59,032
Yunyan secretly

284
00:12:59,032 --> 00:13:00,631
collaborated with the Yanyue Gang.

285
00:13:01,072 --> 00:13:02,831
I mostly turned a blind eye.

286
00:13:03,912 --> 00:13:04,552
But

287
00:13:05,032 --> 00:13:05,631
Lu,

288
00:13:07,471 --> 00:13:09,192
Feng shouldn't have touched Ruoxi.

289
00:13:10,272 --> 00:13:11,072
Do you understand?

290
00:13:16,871 --> 00:13:17,912
Are you so sure

291
00:13:18,351 --> 00:13:19,351
he did it?

292
00:13:51,192 --> 00:13:52,128
Here, Chu Bai.

293
00:13:52,392 --> 00:13:53,192
Have some coffee.

294
00:13:53,711 --> 00:13:55,584
I brewed this pour-over for you.

295
00:14:00,072 --> 00:14:00,992
That's enough.

296
00:14:02,312 --> 00:14:04,552
I know you like Su Yunian,

297
00:14:05,152 --> 00:14:07,192
but I had my reasons
for doing that before.

298
00:14:08,231 --> 00:14:10,471
Now that we're family,

299
00:14:10,751 --> 00:14:11,991
let's put it behind us.

300
00:14:12,871 --> 00:14:13,711
Don't you agree?

301
00:14:16,471 --> 00:14:17,711
Who says we're family?

302
00:14:20,912 --> 00:14:21,952
If we aren't family,

303
00:14:22,511 --> 00:14:23,616
would you sit here?

304
00:14:24,751 --> 00:14:26,072
If we aren't family,

305
00:14:26,871 --> 00:14:28,952
- would you have done these for us?
- Where's Feng?

306
00:14:29,711 --> 00:14:30,631
He promised

307
00:14:31,591 --> 00:14:32,792
once these things are done,

308
00:14:33,471 --> 00:14:34,392
he'll meet me.

309
00:14:37,711 --> 00:14:38,432
Just wait.

310
00:14:38,432 --> 00:14:39,792
I'll go get him.

311
00:14:40,792 --> 00:14:41,351
Hmph.

312
00:14:56,192 --> 00:14:57,831
Quite a sharp-looking young man.

313
00:14:58,991 --> 00:14:59,591
Have a seat.

314
00:15:03,312 --> 00:15:04,351
So you're Feng,

315
00:15:04,991 --> 00:15:05,552
Mr. Nie?

316
00:15:06,511 --> 00:15:07,072
I don't

317
00:15:07,591 --> 00:15:08,312
look the part?

318
00:15:16,072 --> 00:15:16,711
So

319
00:15:17,432 --> 00:15:18,272
scared?

320
00:15:21,072 --> 00:15:22,711
You told my men

321
00:15:23,152 --> 00:15:25,511
the three of us are ruthless killers.

322
00:15:26,032 --> 00:15:28,511
Now you're caught up in our whirlpool.

323
00:15:28,871 --> 00:15:29,952
Not scared at all?

324
00:15:35,111 --> 00:15:36,552
The power of love

325
00:15:37,072 --> 00:15:38,672
is truly unbreakable.

326
00:15:39,072 --> 00:15:40,312
Youngsters are formidable.

327
00:15:42,072 --> 00:15:43,831
You mentioned I told your men.

328
00:15:44,711 --> 00:15:47,871
That security guard, Zhao, is your man?

329
00:15:52,672 --> 00:15:55,711
I meant more than just him.

330
00:15:58,471 --> 00:15:59,631
Did you get the fingerprints?

331
00:16:00,871 --> 00:16:01,631
Got them.

332
00:16:02,991 --> 00:16:04,111
Then things are easier.

333
00:16:06,072 --> 00:16:07,991
I'll handle the arrangements from here.

334
00:16:08,272 --> 00:16:10,631
We'll bring Tu Jiasheng to justice.

335
00:16:11,792 --> 00:16:13,912
But I can't enter Room 999.

336
00:16:14,231 --> 00:16:15,231
No chance to make a move.

337
00:16:17,392 --> 00:16:19,072
Don't worry about that.

338
00:16:20,672 --> 00:16:21,871
Leave it to me.

339
00:16:22,511 --> 00:16:23,351
We'll

340
00:16:24,591 --> 00:16:25,991
hit him

341
00:16:26,511 --> 00:16:32,591
with the diversion trick.

342
00:16:41,856 --> 00:16:45,530
♪If the heart can't hear the sorrow♪

343
00:16:45,829 --> 00:16:49,020
♪It only makes everything look so fake♪

344
00:16:50,688 --> 00:16:54,473
♪Your eyes resemble hers too much♪

345
00:16:55,022 --> 00:16:57,821
♪Who makes me forget whom♪

346
00:16:59,292 --> 00:17:03,022
♪The warmth in my heart is fading♪

347
00:17:03,246 --> 00:17:06,743
♪Every glance feels like atonement♪

348
00:17:08,142 --> 00:17:11,829
♪Ambiguity hidden in the night breeze♪

349
00:17:12,467 --> 00:17:17,582
♪Blows away the chance to explain♪

350
00:17:18,286 --> 00:17:22,420
♪I feel guilty♪

351
00:17:22,990 --> 00:17:26,734
♪I'll have no regrets
even I leave quietly♪

352
00:17:27,598 --> 00:17:31,041
♪Even in tears♪

353
00:17:31,790 --> 00:17:35,704
♪It doesn't matter♪

354
00:17:35,886 --> 00:17:39,709
♪We embrace in dreams♪

355
00:17:40,558 --> 00:17:43,996
♪I let down all my defenses♪

356
00:17:45,152 --> 00:17:48,593
♪Though the story has its end♪

357
00:17:49,358 --> 00:17:56,640
♪I'll journey with you all my life♪
